.SS "template<typename\&.\&.\&. Args> void tuipp::print (const Args &\&.\&.\&. content)"

.PP
Print an output to the screen without a new line at the end (supports markup)\&. 
.SS "Examples:"
.PP
.nf
tuipp::print("[bold green]Hello, World![/]");
tuipp::print("[green]This is green [bold]this is bold and green[/] this is still green[/]");
tuipp::print("[blue]Number of files: [/]", 10, "\&.");
tuipp::print("[green]This is green [bold]this is bold and green[reset] this is normal");
.fi
.PP
.SS "Styles:"
.IP "\(bu" 2
Foreground colors: \fRred\fP, \fRgreen\fP, \fRgrey\fP, \fRblue\fP, \fRmagenta\fP, \fRyellow\fP, \fRwhite\fP, \fRbright_red\fP, \fRbright_green\fP, \fRbright_grey\fP, \fRbright_blue\fP, \fRbright_magenta\fP, \fRbright_yellow\fP, \fRbright_cyan\fP, \fRbright_white\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Background colors: \fRbg_red\fP, \fRbg_green\fP, \fRbg_grey\fP, \fRbg_blue\fP, \fRbg_magenta\fP, \fRbg_yellow\fP, \fRbg_cyan\fP, \fRbg_white\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Effects: \fRbold\fP, \fRunderline\fP, \fRblink\fP, \fRitalic\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Reset: \fR/\fP, \fRreset\fP
.PP

.PP
.PP

.PP
You can also escape markup brackets using a backslash:

.PP
.PP
.nf
tuipp::print("\\[bold red]Hello, World!\\[/]");
.fi
.PP

.PP
\fBParameters\fP
.RS 4
\fIcontent\fP The items you want to print, they can be of any type and you can pass as many as you want\&. 
.RE
.PP

.SS "template<typename\&.\&.\&. Args> void tuipp::println (const Args &\&.\&.\&. content)"

.PP
Print an output to the screen with a new line at the end (supports markup)\&. 
.SS "Examples:"
.PP
.nf
tuipp::println("[bold green]Hello, World![reset]");
tuipp::println(
"[green]This is green [bold]this is bold and green[/] this is still green[reset]"
);
tuipp::println("[blue]Number of files: [reset]", 10, "\&.");
tuipp::println("[green]This is green [bold]this is bold and green[reset] this is normal");
.fi
.PP
.SS "Styles:"
.IP "\(bu" 2
Foreground colors: \fRred\fP, \fRgreen\fP, \fRgrey\fP, \fRblue\fP, \fRmagenta\fP, \fRyellow\fP, \fRwhite\fP, \fRbright_red\fP, \fRbright_green\fP, \fRbright_grey\fP, \fRbright_blue\fP, \fRbright_magenta\fP, \fRbright_yellow\fP, \fRbright_cyan\fP, \fRbright_white\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Background colors: \fRbg_red\fP, \fRbg_green\fP, \fRbg_grey\fP, \fRbg_blue\fP, \fRbg_magenta\fP, \fRbg_yellow\fP, \fRbg_cyan\fP, \fRbg_white\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Effects: \fRbold\fP, \fRunderline\fP, \fRblink\fP, \fRitalic\fP
.IP "\(bu" 2
Reset: \fR/\fP (for one style), \fRreset\fP (for all the styles)
.PP

